(31) “week” means the period of seven days beginning at mid-night on Saturday; 

(32) “winter” means the period covering the months of October, November, December, 
January, February and March; 

(33) “year” means the calendar year; 

(34) “young person” means a person who is not a child and has not completed his 
eighteenth year of age. 
